    "This process is illustrated in Fig. 3.",
    "LLM tokenizes the input text and converts them into numerical representations, which are then fed into the transformer encoder for language comprehension.",
    "We follow transfer learning to re-train or fine-tune the models with the adult learning dataset.",
    "This process adjusts the weights of various layers in the transformer architecture.",
    "Specifically, we can freeze some layers near the input and fine-tune the rest layers near the output."
